data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful Ranch is on a .5 acre lot, features a spacious Open concept living space with tons of room to entertain. Recently painted throughtout, formal living room with fireplace, amazing and cozy sunroom with access to the large backyard and fire pit. Primary Bedroom with separate bathroom, and down the hall is a bathroom with two perfectly sized bedrooms. The kitchen is large and in charge with an island, open shelves, and tons of storage, where you can be preparing a meal for your guests and still being a part of the festivities. This house has been love and cherished! Only minutes away from Halcyon and interstate 400 with no HOA. Get the wonderful living experience in this amazing property and see how close its is to shopping and entertainment!
